overview: Inside the walls of Xtrem club, these chics and young sexy women satisfy their fantasies of double penetration.  You could meet them in the elevator or at work, on the benches of the college or near the coffee machine... Women today, our four heroines lead a busy life, leaving nothing to guess their personal livies. Yet, they all share the same secret... For the first time, they experienced the magic of libertine life: an invitation to the club Xtrem, a place of all fantasies! The time of a few hours, between the walls of this very select club, they can loosen up and let themselves in the hands of expert lovers who fill all their holes. Some are shy, others more adventurous, but all are terribly excited at the prospect of finally taking the plunge.
